		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><small> <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/0.9_(Ma)" title="0.9 (Ma)">‹———— 0.9</a> &#8195; <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/0.7_(Lindqvist)" title="0.7 (Lindqvist)">0.7 ————›</a> </small> <br />
<a class="mw-selflink selflink">0.8 (Romero)</a> is a version of Cataclysm that was released on 2013 September 16.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
